asset.title: Converse CONS Coach’s Waffle Fleece Jacket
asset.description:
Inspired by the late 80’s/early 90’s adoption of sportswear in skate culture the essential 100% cotton jacket is perfect for complete freedom of motion. Crafted with a textured double knit fabric with a waffle knit on the interior for warmth and durability, concealed pockets with forward facing side seam, double folded heavyweight rib cuff, classic draw cord with metal tips and is secured with snaps. Skating by Jerome Campbell and Ollie Lock.

Dungeon Acid  
https://www.huhtahomestudio.bandcamp.com
